<h2><b>How to Choose a Crypto Trading Bot</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The best crypto AI trading application in 2026 depends less on “which platform is number one” and more on </span><b>how you want to trade</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Different platforms are built for different levels of experience, automation needs, and strategy control.</span></p>
