<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Coinrule and Altrady excel in this area, offering no-code or advanced rule engines.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Best for traders who want logic-driven automation</span></p>
<h3><b>4. Signal and Copy Trading Models</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Signal-based trading connects your bot to external trading signals, while copy trading allows you to replicate strategies from experienced traders.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">WunderTrading and Cryptohopper support these features, enabling users to follow proven strategies.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Best for users who prefer guided or semi-automated trading</span></p>
<h3><b>5. Fully Automated Trading Systems</b></h3>
